&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;In this role, you will provide day-to-day support for the VP for EMEA, ensuring they can operate efficiently and stay focused on top priorities. You will manage complex scheduling across multiple time zones, coordinate travel and expenses, and support key team activities including meetings, offsites, and reporting. You&#39;ll play a central role in keeping the leadership team organized, informed, and moving forward by anticipating needs, driving follow-ups, and handling sensitive information with discretion.&lt;/p&gt;
