&lt;li&gt;Clear written and verbal communication, documentation skills, and readiness to participate in an on-call rotation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High curiosity to deeply learn specialized GPU interconnect technologies such as NVLink, NVSwitch, and InfiniBand.&lt;/li&gt;
