&lt;li&gt;Deep, hands-on experience building real-time distributed systems under strict latency, scale, and resilience constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical intuition for where legacy architectures break down at scale, with the creativity to invent new approaches rather than simply extending existing ones.&lt;/li&gt;
