&lt;li&gt;Skilled at identifying capability gaps between customer workflows and existing platform features, building strategic cross-functional alignment to resolve them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in navigating full-stack architectural design, with a strong understanding of bare-metal topologies, orchestration layers, and application APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
