&lt;li&gt;Solid technical background in cloud networking infrastructure, including VPCs, routing, security policies, and overlay/underlay networking topologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to build testing, simulation, and automation frameworks from scratch using Python, Golang, or similar systems languages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency in network observability, low-level benchmarking, and deep production troubleshooting using tools like tcpdump, iproute2, and perf.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and technical leadership skills, with a track record of driving technical direction and mentoring engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
